# NOTE: quack/*/*.duckdb_extension.gz ARE committed (unlike solid, which
# fetches at build time): the SDK is consumed as a Go module, and the module
# zip must carry the //go:embed payload or every consumer importing quack
# fails to build (the v0.6.0 lesson — retracted). scripts/duckdb-fetch.sh is
# the refresh/verify tool for pin bumps, not a build prerequisite.

